OL,3,CAlan Bates urges subpostmasters to
OL,4,Ctake government to court over redress
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,FSir Alan Bates has urged victims of
OL,8,Fthe Horizon scandal to take the
OL,9,FGovernment to court over delays to
OL,10,Ffinancial redress.
OL,12,FIn an email sent to members of
OL,13,Fcampaign group Justice For
OL,14,FSubpostmasters Alliance (JFSA), seen
OL,15,Fby ITV News, Sir Alan said a judicial
OL,16,Freview would "probably be the quickest
OL,17,Fway to ensure fairness for all".
OL,19,FHe told the group it would likely take
OL,20,Funtil November 2027 for all claims to
OL,21,Fbe completed.
