OL,7,FMore than 900 subpostmasters were
OL,8,Fprosecuted between 1999 and 2015 after
OL,9,Ffaulty Horizon accounting software
OL,10,Fmade it look as though money was
OL,11,Fmissing from their accounts.
OL,13,FMany are still awaiting compensation
OL,14,Fdespite the previous government
OL,15,Fannouncing that those who have had
OL,16,Fconvictions quashed are eligible for
OL,17,F#600,000 payouts.
