OL,7,FSir Alan told JFSA members it was
OL,8,F"time for others to step up", adding:
OL,9,F"Hopefully you'll all agree I've done
OL,10,Fmy bit."
OL,12,FChristopher Head, who became the
OL,13,FBritain's youngest subpostmaster in
OL,14,F2006 at the age of 18, offered his
OL,15,Fassistance in taking the Department
OL,16,Ffor Business and Trade (DBT) to court
OL,17,Fbecause he had already aired his case
OL,18,F"out in public on purpose to be
OL,19,Ftransparent".
