OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,FIn his "JFSA Circular", Sir Alan
OL,8,Fdescribed the group litigation order
OL,9,F(GLO) scheme, which was set up to
OL,10,Fachieve redress for the 555 claimants
OL,11,Fwho took the Post Office to the High
OL,12,FCourt between 2017 and 2019, as a
OL,13,F"mess", a claim the Government denies.
OL,15,FIn his email, Sir Alan said: "There
OL,16,Fmay be other options but the one which
OL,17,Fis repeatedly mentioned is a judicial
OL,18,Freview, not just for the GLO scheme
OL,19,Fbut to include all of the schemes to
OL,20,Fensure there is parity in the way
OL,21,Fvictims have, and are, being treated.
