OL,3,CAlan Bates urges subpostmasters to
OL,4,Ctake government to court over redress
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,F"Returning to the courts may seem to
OL,8,Fbe a long haul, but it will probably
OL,9,Fbe (the) quickest way to ensure
OL,10,Ffairness for all."
OL,12,FHis email added: "I do know many of
OL,13,Fyou who have already settled have done
OL,14,Fso out of desperation or despair or
OL,15,Fbecause you have been backed into a
OL,16,Fcorner to accept an offer.
OL,18,F"Well a new legal action may well be a
OL,19,Fway of having your claim reassessed
OL,20,Fonce more, this time by the courts."
