OL,7,FReferring to the GLO scheme, Sir Alan
OL,8,Fsaid: "Quite simply the scheme is a
OL,9,Fmess, and has been almost since the
OL,10,Ftime of its inception.
OL,12,F"Advice on how to streamline and speed
OL,13,Fup the scheme which has been offered
OL,14,Fto the DBT by ourselves, your lawyers
OL,15,Fand even the DBT select committee is
OL,16,Fignored out of hand with the feeblest
OL,17,Fof excuses.
