OL,7,FA Government spokesperson told ITV
OL,8,FNews it "pays tribute to all the
OL,9,Fpostmaster who have suffered due to
OL,10,Fthe Horizon software over the past 25
OL,11,Fyears".
OL,13,FThey added that the Government is
OL,14,Fworking "at pace" to ensure
OL,15,Fsubposmaster receive redress.
OL,17,F"However, we do not accept this
OL,18,Fforecast. The facts show we are making
OL,19,Falmost 90% of initial GLO offers
OL,20,Fwithin 40 working days of receiving
OL,21,Fcompleted claims," they continued.
